ubtle, sweet flavour. You can find it in health food stores or Asian food stores.","Celtic sea salt may contain a number of minerals and trace elements. You can find it in health food stores and some gourmet food stores. You could also use standard sea salt in this recipe.","We recommend marinating tofu in a rectangular or square baking dish so that the tofu can lay flat and better absorb the marinade.","Store wakame gomasio in a sealable container in a cool, dark place. Use it to season steamed rice and vegetables, as a dukkah or to flavour popcorn.","For a heartier meal, serve with steamed rice or udon noodles.","This recipe contains a number of nutrients, including calcium, zinc, vitamin C and protein."],"basicInfo":["easy","25m","2h 25m","4 portions"]}